          "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>The Knifetooth firebrand surrounds itself with an aura of violet flame, shedding &amp;Reference[rule=brightlight]{bright light} in a 10-foot radius and &amp;Reference[rule=dimlight]{dim light} for an additional 10 feet. These flames increase the firebrand's AC by 1. Whenever a creature within 10 feet of the firebrand hits it with an attack, the flames leap to the attacker, dealing that attacker 5 ([[/damage 2d4 type=fire]]) damage. Violet flame outlines a creature struck by this fire, so the creature gains no benefit from being &amp;Reference[condition=invisible] until it leaves the aura. This aura lasts for 10 minutes, until the firebrand uses this action again, until the firebrand is &amp;Reference[condition=incapacitated] or dies, or until the firebrand uses a bonus action to end it.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div>",
